{"tid":493103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[法律JJ請進] 聽唔到警察按門鐘，之後佢地走左，咁我有無事？","createTime":"2017-12-08T08:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T11:05:43.000Z","uid":57376,"like":3,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"2b32155716a1594459657f158f16eb5aa890a6ee","tid":493103,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:01:57.000Z","msg":"尋晚打機打到半路，突然聽到出面好似有人按門鐘，但撞正我打到危急關頭走唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後過多幾十秒左右我終於打贏果關，即刻走出去睇下個防盜鏡，見到三個警察離開緊，咁我又覺得好似無必要叫佢返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但而家諗諗下又有D擔心，其實我係咪應該開門俾佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43020abf9652e8f50db1c90d58e98619002c2093","tid":493103,"uid":127870,"like":159,"dislike":0,"score":159,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:03:08.000Z","msg":"放心<br />\n有事搵你佢地會再返黎"},{"pid":"63ea3b7434ae150f8b86994616351a619d82162b","tid":493103,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:03:12.000Z","msg":"如果有緊要事搵我，應該都會有其他通知掛？<br />\n<br />\n但等到而家都無任何電話、通告之類<br />\n<br />\n係咪我諗多左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5eddf09427f0e16354df23659ff626df6fe5256","tid":493103,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e845326c9e92a71a753e81adbc260bd95074f4","tid":493103,"uid":122745,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:04:02.000Z","msg":"你打機聲浪太嘈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f543f6a640006b731c62afab3af1954d9d7feb62","tid":493103,"uid":57376,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:04:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放心<br />\n有事搵你佢地會再返黎</blockquote><br />\n點解唔打電話俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到我成日都心掛掛<img src=\"/assets